# Kairos Environment Configuration
#
# Copy to `.env` and uncomment variables as needed.
# Most users need no changes — sensible defaults are built in.

# ─── Logging ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Module-level log filters. Comma-separated.
# RUST_LOG=kairos_data=debug

# ─── Rithmic Server URLs (optional) ──────────────────────────
# By default, Kairos resolves Rithmic WebSocket endpoints
# automatically via https://kairos.org. No configuration
# is required for most users.
#
# To use direct Rithmic endpoints instead, uncomment and set
# the servers you need. Contact Rithmic (rithmic.com) for
# production WebSocket URLs associated with your account.
#
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_CHICAGO=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_NEW_YORK=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_SYDNEY=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_SAO_PAOLO=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_COLO75=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_FRANKFURT=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_HONG_KONG=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_IRELAND=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_MUMBAI=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_SEOUL=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_CAPE_TOWN=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_TOKYO=wss://...
# KAIROS_RITHMIC_SERVER_SINGAPORE=wss://...

# Override the server-resolution API endpoint (advanced).
# KAIROS_SERVER_API_URL=https://kairos.org
